Sentencas: The effect of co-doping of Sr and Al or Fe on the microstructure, sinterability and oxide-ion conductivity of lanthanum silicate oxyapatites is investigated in detail at 300-800 degrees C by the electrochemical impedance spectroscopy.

Sentencas: The results indicate that co-doping of Sr and Al or Fe significantly improves the densification, sinterability and oxide-ion conductivity of lanthanum silicate oxyapatites.
